channel.title: Some one changed my password i need help!
channel.description:
Hi my moparscape account name is blood_pker54. I was on it last night till around 2:00am in the morning. I live in new york. I am unable to get in today at all. It keeps saying password invalid. Since i can not provide you with any other information to help you get it back for me I can tell u what is in bank well most of it. I had 1708k whips, 1,808k zerker rings, 105k santas, 110k blue and green masks, 10k red masks,around 55k to 60k fire capes, alot of barrows armor, about 39 phat sets. I dont know if this can help me get , my account back, but i really would like it back. It was working fine this morning, but when i went on today at around 11:00am it didnt work. So please help me out with this. I want to continue playing!!
Get back to me as soon as possible!
